<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>KnowMore Account Activation</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset styles */
        body, html {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        /* Container styles */
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
        /* Header styles */
        .header {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
        }
        /* Content styles */
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        /* Button styles */
        .btn {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        /* Footer styles */
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #777;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>KnowMore Account Activation</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <%= user.name %>,</p>
            <p>Welcome to KnowMore! You're just one step away from activating your account.</p>
            <p>Please find activation Code below to activate your account:</p>
            <h2> <%= activationCode %> </h2>
            <p>If you didn't request this, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>If you have any questions, please contact support at <a href="mailto:support@knowmore.com">support@knowmore</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
